---
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Map - Visualize the Data" currentPage="visualize">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <a href="/visualize" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-focus flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
        Back to Visualizations
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Map</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p class="mb-8 text-lg max-w-xl">
      Explore the geographic distribution of events and data points. This interactive map visualization helps you understand spatial patterns and regional variations.
    </p>

    <!-- Placeholder Content -->
    <div class="grid gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="p-6 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Coming Soon</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The Map visualization is currently under development. This page will feature:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>Interactive geographic map with data points</li>
          <li>Zoom and pan controls for exploration</li>
          <li>Filterable layers and categories</li>
          <li>Detailed location information and context</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Sample Map Location</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Coordinates: 40.7128° N, 74.0060° W</p>
          <h4 class="font-medium">Sample Location: New York City</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            This is a placeholder for a map location that would show the geographic distribution of events in our dataset. 
            The actual map will be populated with real locations and data points.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-accent text-white text-xs rounded">Event Type</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 text-xs rounded">Date Range</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">About the Map</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        The Map visualization will provide a spatial perspective on the data, allowing researchers to identify geographic patterns, 
        regional variations, and spatial relationships between different events and data points.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout> 